{"tid":447252,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟蜜瓜包係味真係有蜜瓜味？","createTime":"2017-10-25T06:17:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T04:49:19.000Z","uid":118467,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"84ff2f87eb9c11d885186106827837c69403907e","tid":447252,"uid":118467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T06:17:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/141541_98995ef9a940fc6bc19aee37e7341b02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F141541_98995ef9a940fc6bc19aee37e7341b02.jpg&h=737808fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說我朋友話蜜瓜包係蜜瓜味所以叫蜜瓜包<br />\n我就屌作話菠蘿包唔通又菠蘿味咩？<br />\n佢就屌番我話蜜瓜包真係蜜瓜味<br />\n究竟蜜瓜包真係有蜜瓜味先叫蜜瓜包定係個樣似蜜瓜先叫蜜瓜包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4dbf23b679509055938527adc23b6b321cff5fe","tid":447252,"uid":83798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T06:19:34.000Z","msg":"認真<br />\n係似蜜瓜"},{"pid":"514e255cfd93bdba8828f41bc451acab17ff952d","tid":447252,"uid":109604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T06:25:13.000Z","msg":"其實真係有蜜瓜味 所以先叫蜜瓜包"},{"pid":"21a70d283e614ea9690476bbd1f6b43100d78f48","tid":447252,"uid":118467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T06:30:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實真係有蜜瓜味 所以先叫蜜瓜包</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係個樣似蜜瓜囉，唔識就唔好亂講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7eb5e83c6dfde75109614d3df99b95091ce7369","tid":447252,"uid":15823,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T06:34:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-eqZYiOgXDnI/VlxM7LByNAI/AAAAAAAAfxU/V5jd3FEcFSA/s450-Ic42/0000-391798.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2F-eqZYiOgXDnI%2FVlxM7LByNAI%2FAAAAAAAAfxU%2FV5jd3FEcFSA%2Fs450-Ic42%2F0000-391798.jpg&h=de3b6955&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9cf15bc735e26641daf98dd984747ec7aef17f37","tid":447252,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T06:38:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb1339e7d18791f9192d3e980c9503826e4dd0b3","tid":447252,"uid":88235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T06:40:35.000Z","msg":"係日本買過有d真係會落蜜瓜汁去整<br />\n所以會有好香嘅蜜瓜味"},{"pid":"e2cc9a6c29c2da5706e818a3b2a228cdb3d95d12","tid":447252,"uid":109604,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T06:45:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係日本買過有d真係會落蜜瓜汁去整<br />\n所以會有好香嘅蜜瓜味</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無錯<br />\n58號 哈密瓜壽司麵包<br />\n上層的餅皮與下層的麵包分開烘烤，以像是壽司的方式將哈密瓜果汁夾在中間"},{"pid":"4b5ac651e5662c71cacd093f6a623b83bbc05d87","tid":447252,"uid":83798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T13:19:37.000Z","msg":"係日本買過啲得甜味冇蜜瓜味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8da7dd0938c07270ee7dee56fe2640b4482c7f1","tid":447252,"uid":118467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T02:38:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係日本買過有d真係會落蜜瓜汁去整<br />\n所以會有好香嘅蜜瓜味</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無錯<br />\n58號 哈密瓜壽司麵包<br />\n上層的餅皮與下層的麵包分開烘烤，以像是壽司的方式將哈密瓜果汁夾在中間</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n收聲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e336381ca62007719e3827574599731961317d1","tid":447252,"uid":138834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:49:19.000Z","msg":"正宗：因為似蜜瓜而叫蜜瓜包<br />\n後來：反正都係叫蜜瓜包，不如試下加啲蜜瓜味入去<br />\n<br />\n依家嚟講，應該仲係冇蜜瓜味嘅比較多"}]}